<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About click'n'debrid</h1>

  <div class="card p-6 mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start mb-6">
      <img src="/img/logo.svg" alt="click'n'debrid Logo" class="h-32 w-32 mx-auto md:mx-0 mb-4 md:mb-0 md:mr-6">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">click'n'debrid</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Version <%= version %></p>
        <p class="opacity-75">A Click'n'Load proxy server that converts links via debrid services API and submits them
          to PyLoad et al.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Overview</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">
      click'n'debrid serves as an intermediary between Click'n'Load compatible browser extensions and download managers
      like PyLoad.
      It automatically processes links through debrid services to provide premium download links, enhancing your
      downloading experience
      without manual intervention.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Features</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Intercepts Click'n'Load requests from browser extensions</li>
      <li>Processes file links through debrid services (e.g., Real-Debrid)</li>
      <li>Forwards converted premium links to your download manager</li>
      <li>Caches processed packages for easy management</li>
      <li>Supports both Redis and in-memory caching</li>
      <li>Modern admin interface for managing packages</li>
    </ul>

