      This means you can freely use, modify, and distribute this software, provided you include the original license
      and copyright notice with any distribution.
    </p>

    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <p class="opacity-75">Created by XaverLeet</p>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-50 mt-2">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> All Rights Reserved</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>